24:49.722 --> 24:52.214
Ms. Hillary Rodham
of Chicago,

24:52.291 --> 24:53.690
and a connection.

24:53.759 --> 24:55.659
There'll be a connection?

24:55.728 --> 24:57.218
I believe there will be.

24:57.296 --> 24:59.162
This really isn't
political, is it?

24:59.231 --> 25:00.858
No, sir, it is not.

25:00.933 --> 25:04.062
<i>You have a crush
on Hillary Clinton.</i>

25:04.136 --> 25:05.729
