that's four. Casey and Dan.

25:53.185 --> 25:54.311
-- That's six.
-- Thanks.

25:54.386 --> 25:55.376
Will, Chris, and Dave --

25:55.454 --> 25:58.321
-- I'm just doing this in my head,
but that's nine, right? -- Yes.

25:58.390 --> 26:00.324
Isaac, good, you're here.

26:00.392 --> 26:02.520
