26:11.303 --> 26:13.533
-- <i>Just as</i> good <i>in</i> my book.
-- <i>30 seconds live.</i>

26:13.605 --> 26:15.733
-- Isaac, tell these people, would you?
-- Tell them what?

26:15.808 --> 26:16.969
Tell them the rumor
isn't true.

26:17.042 --> 26:20.569
Tell them there isn't a ratings
expert coming in to work on the show.

26:20.646 --> 26:21.875
The rumor <i>is</i> true.

26:22.948 --> 26:26.646
There <i>is</i> a ratings expert coming to work
on the show, and he's coming tomorrow.

26:26.719 --> 26:29.211
The network
hired a ratings guy?

26:29.288 --> 26:32.189
The network didn't hire him.
I did.

26:32.257 --> 26:34.282
Dana, this may not be
the right time,

26:34.393 --> 26:36.361
but that's 10.

26:36.395 --> 26:38.454
In 3...2...

26:38.530 --> 26:39.759
Good evening.
From New York City,

26:39.832 --> 26:42.267
I'm Casey McCall
alongside Dan Rydell.

26:42.334 --> 26:44.268
<i>Those stories, plus we'll
take you around the NHL,</i>

26:44.336 --> 26:47.567
<i>where the Red Wings did some
damage to the duck pond,</i>

26:47.639 --> 26:49.300
and we'll take you
around the NFL,

26:49.375 --> 26:51.844
where the Dolphins did
some damage to themselves.

26:51.910 --> 26:53.344
All that coming up after this.

26:53.412 --> 26:56.347
You're watching “Sports Night“
on CSC, so stick around.

26:56.415 --> 26:58.076
<i>Dave." We're out.</i>

26:58.150 --> 27:00.050
Ever been
on a carriage ride?

27:00.119 --> 27:02.588
